IP Policy of Peripheral Arbor, and All Work of Paul Spooner

Source: https://ip.tryop.com

I, Paul Daniel Spooner, born 1984-01-11, on this the fifth of August,
the Year of Our Lord two thousand and fourteen (2014-08-05) hereby
release the entirety of my intellectual property to the public domain.
All ideas which I have produced in the past, or will produce in the
future, I hereby make available for the free and unrestricted use by
all people for all time. I explicitly forbid any entity, regardless of
merit, standing, or interest, from restricting the free and unaltered
dissemination of any information which falls under my authority.
Anyone may use, employ, adapt, and/or transform any concept I have
produced for any purpose without fear of retribution or litigation
originating from myself.

— Paul Spooner
